name: oov1wq legacy anime prompt style
description:
oov1wq legacy hypernetwork

This is not my work and I don't plan to support this, just trying to preserve this Hypernetwork for the community.

What does it do?

Makes things more anime-like and seems to push them into the sitting position..? Or maybe it's my imagination.

It seems impossible to make guys with this at 1.0 as well.. it drags everything into 'young anime female'

Doesn't seem to have any preference for NSFW but marking it as such just in case.

Why though?

If you don't know what this is for or why you want it - you probably don't need it.

I run into several prompts a day that use this thing and it was impossible to find..

Credits

No idea who made this or what artwork inspired it..
